snippet.title: Myth II: Soulblighter Official Trailer - Bungie
snippet.description:
An Official Myth II trailer taken from a review copy of Myth II's Press kit.

If you would like to play Myth now, find a copy online, and get the newest update from http://projectmagma.net/

Then sign up at http://mariusnet.com to play it online. See you around!
